般从 1 月 20 日（1 月下旬）开始，1 月下旬恰是南方一年中最冷的时候。小寒胜大寒，冬深春不远"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-f9c202c998cfcf645c0bd34110bf8e04_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "47 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/576654372"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIyq3y8qmwjdpwEAMaCDkwNDI2OTIzIKGA1J0GMAA4JEAtcgk1NzY2NTQzNzJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "46_1672888137.009387", "card_id": "Q_576665215", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 11}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "山东医院回应 4000 元招募新冠患者，称「共需来医院 10 趟，检查费用全免」，如何看待此事？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，淄博市第一医院发布《招募新型冠状病毒肺炎患者》。@大河报记者向该医院咨询招募新冠患者一事，工作人员称所用药物系武汉传染病医院研发，所招募的新冠患者一人补贴 4000 元，共需来医院 10 趟，抽血 3 次吃药 5 天，检查费用全免。目前，只要符合要求的意向患者，即可前往医院。 来源 大河报"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-08e835bd6d019cb755be5574ee06b530_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "47 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/576665215"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIyq3y8qmwjdpwEAMaCDkwNDI5MzI0IMy01J0GMAA4E0Aucgk1NzY2NjUyMTV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1672888137.010234", "card_id": "Q_576650924", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 56}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "除了呼吸道和肺部之外，未来新冠毒株进化后是否会主要攻击其他器官或系统？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-33073a68c7313ef427f586cdaaa50c2b_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "47 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu